room_title: Escape room "CheckMate" by Michigan Escape Games in Davison
room_description: Lured by promises from the “ToyMaker”, you find yourselves locked in a room full of nostalgic games, toys and sports. The only way for you to escape is to find the ToyMaker’s most prized possession and return it in under 75 minutes lest you be added to his ‘collection’.
